General.Description: W&T Offshore, Inc., an independent oil and natural gas producer, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of oil and natural gas properties in the Gulf of America. The company sells crude oil, condensate, natural gas, and natural gas liquids. W&T Offshore, Inc. was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas.
